{"title": "Concrete Features", "body": {"ops": [{"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a", "underline": true}, "insert": "Concrete Features"}, {"attributes": {"header": 2}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "Considering the "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "previous feature set"}, {"insert": ", we laid out the following feature set required by the final product, on top of a basic editor:\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Simple JavaScript modules"}, {"insert": ": One can load "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "JavaScript"}, {"insert": " files in the app to extend functionality easily."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Interlinked notes"}, {"insert": ": One should be able to write "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "links "}, {"insert": "between notes, in order to better organise "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "related concepts"}, {"insert": " in the app."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Support for "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": {"formula": "\\LaTeX"}}, {"insert": " : One ought to be able to type"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": {"formula": "\\LaTeX"}}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " "}, {"insert": "expressions, for the taking of more "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "mathematically sophisticated"}, {"insert": " notes."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Intelligent search"}, {"insert": ": The search function must be able to consider the "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "semantic contents"}, {"insert": " of notes, and return results"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " based on these similarities"}, {"insert": "."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "An accessible UI"}, {"insert": ": The app should accommodate for "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "users with access needs"}, {"insert": ", in particular being accessible to users who use "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "screen readers"}, {"insert": ", or who use a"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " different standard font size"}, {"insert": " on their web browser.\n\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_2"}, "insert": "previous slide"}, {"insert": " | "}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_4"}, "insert": "next slide"}, {"attributes": {"align": "center"}, "insert": "\n"}]}, "text": "Concrete Features\n\nConsidering the previous feature set, we laid out the following feature set required by the final product, on top of a basic editor:\n\n\n\n\nSimple JavaScript modules: One can load JavaScript files in the app to extend functionality easily.\n\n\n\n\nInterlinked notes: One should be able to write links between notes, in order to better organise related concepts in the app.\n\n\n\n\nSupport for \ufeff\nLaTeX\nL\nA\nT\nE\n\t\u200b\n\nX\ufeff : One ought to be able to type \ufeff\nLaTeX\nL\nA\nT\nE\n\t\u200b\n\nX\ufeff expressions, for the taking of more mathematically sophisticated notes.\n\n\n\n\nIntelligent search: The search function must be able to consider the semantic contents of notes, and return results based on these similarities.\n\n\n\n\nAn accessible UI: The app should accommodate for users with access needs, in particular being accessible to users who use screen readers, or who use a different standard font size on their web browser.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nprevious slide | next slide", "updatedAt": 1715122135397}